  • Constructor Details

    • ClientConfiguration

      public ClientConfiguration​(java.lang.String userId, java.lang.String url, int port, int timeout, java.lang.String userPrivateKey, java.lang.String serverPublicKey, java.lang.String adminEmail)
      Create a client configuration object.
      Parameters:
      userId - The user related to the client
      url - Server URL
      port - Server port
      timeout - Connection timeout. If 0, the timeout is defaulted to 10 seconds.
      userPrivateKey - THe private RSA key of the user as a base64-encoded string
      serverPublicKey - The public RSA key of the server as a base64-encoded string
      adminEmail - The e-mail address of the server administrator
